I would disagree with putting all the points into FD.  FD is very easy to skill up.  Hell, I had a macro that would FD, ID, and sneak all in one.  Just target a group member and hit it now and then.

Or, if you don't want to worry about the accidental ID causing a feared mob to run away starting a train...then just hit FD every time it pops up...even while running.

Hell, I advise making a macro that makes you FD and then stand up again to work on it.  It's great to have when running away from a MOB but you don't want to waste time finding the stand button (or hitting CTRL-S) in case it fails.

However, MEND is a bitch to skill up.  Definately put as many points into it as you can...it's worth it.

